Summary: Bright Light That Moved At IncredibleSpeed

I saw what I that was a star but is was larger, not quite as bright and just above the tree line. I thought , that is not right, there is no star supposed to be there. Within a few seconds it moved across the skyline to the southeast and then went behind a tree line where I could not see it.
